p.d: Hispania Rally took place in Guadix – Granada in 2020. It achieved to host more than 180 participants from more than 26 countries. What the Hispania Rally strong as well as unique is the hard to drive, Gorafe desert. This extraordinary location has led the Hispania Rally to be recognized as the only European rally that takes place in the sandy and hot desert.
